<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>com.qrcodegen.app</id>
  <metadata_license>MIT</metadata_license>
  <project_license>MIT</project_license>
  <name>QrCodeGen</name>
  <summary>Batch generate QR codes with logo from Excel</summary>
  <description>
    <p>QrCodeGen is a powerful batch QR code generator that supports importing data from Excel files, customizing QR code styles, adding logos, and supports multiple export formats.</p>
    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Batch QR code generation</li>
      <li>Excel import support</li>
      <li>Custom logo and styles</li>
      <li>Multiple export formats (PNG, JPG, SVG, PDF)</li>
      <li>Built-in QR code decoder</li>
      <li>Chinese and English interface support</li>
    </ul>
    <p xml:lang="zh">QrCodeGen 是一款功能强大的批量二维码生成工具，支持从 Excel 文件导入数据，自定义二维码样式、添加 Logo，并支持多种导出格式。</p>
    <p xml:lang="zh">主要功能：</p>
    <ul>
      <li xml:lang="zh">批量生成二维码</li>
      <li xml:lang="zh">支持 Excel 导入</li>
      <li xml:lang="zh">自定义 Logo 和样式</li>
      <li xml:lang="zh">多种导出格式（PNG、JPG、SVG、PDF）</li>
      <li xml:lang="zh">内置二维码解码功能</li>
      <li xml:lang="zh">支持中英文界面</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
